microservice-order

info:
1；microservice-order子项目为springcloud的订单微服务
2；集成了rabbitmq作为消息中间件
3；核心依赖为：
                    <dependency>
                        <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
                        <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-amqp</artifactId>
                    </dependency>
4：yml配置为：
      spring:
        rabbitmq:
            host: 127.0.0.1
            port: 5672
            username: guest
            password: guest
            connection-timeout: 2000ms
            publisher-confirms: true  #生产者确认消息  confirmListener
            publisher-returns: true   #消息未被消费则原封不动返回，不被处理  returnListener
            listener:
              simple:
                acknowledge-mode: manual
                retry:
                  enabled: true
                  max-attempts: 3

 note:
 1：简单实现了rabbitmq的topic模式，消息确认机制，死信队列的使用